{"version":"1.2","person":{"datePublished":"2023-12-14","name":"Ture Kettilsson Bielke af Åkerö","nameForms":[{"lang":"sv","fullText":"Ture Kettilsson Bielke af Åkerö","parts":[{"type":"http://gedcomx.org/Given","value":"Ture"},{"type":"http://gedcomx.org/Surname","value":"Kettilsson"},{"type":"http://gedcomx.org/Suffix","value":"Bielke af Åkerö"}],"order":"EUROTYPIC"}],"gender":"Male","lifespan":"1260–1327","fullLifespan":"1260–29 March 1327","portrait":{"url":"https://tree-portraits-pgp.familysearchcdn.org/5e18k/thumb200s.jpg","@type":"ImageObject"},"memoryArtifacts":[{"memoryType":"PHOTO","url":"https://sg30p0.familysearch.org/service/records/storage/dascloud/patron/v2/TH-7769-125043-3707-5/dist.jpg?ctx=ArtCtxPublic","memoryUrl":"https://www.familysearch.org/photos/artifacts/171580651","thumbnailUrl":"https://sg30p0.familysearch.org/service/records/storage/dascloud/patron/v2/TH-7769-125043-3707-5/thumb200s.jpg?ctx=ArtCtxPublic","deepZoomUrl":"https://sg30p0.familysearch.org/service/records/storage/deepzoomcloud/dzpatron/v1/TH-7769-125043-3707-5/scale?ctx=ArtCtxPublic","headline":"Ture Kettilsson Bielke","@type":"ImageObject"}],"birthDate":"+1260","deathDate":"+1327-03-29","deathPlace":{"address":"Kråkerum, Mönsterås, Kalmar, Sverige","geo":{"latitude":57.05,"longitude":16.45,"@type":"GeoCoordinates"},"@type":"Place"},"userCertifiedLifeSummary":"\"Tures hustru hette Sigrid och överlevde honom. Enligt uppgift av den gamle genealogen Utter, som sett ett av henne beseglat, numera förlorat brev av år 1327, förde hon en sparre i vapnet; uppgiften kan möjligen anses bekräftad därav, att Tures söner bevisligen voro släkt med den från konung Magnus Erikssons tid bekante Ulf Abjörnsson (sparre).\"\n\n\"Ture's wife's name was Sigrid and she survived him. According to information from the old genealogist Utter, who saw a letter sealed by her, now lost, from the year 1327, she carried a spar in her weapon; the information can possibly be considered confirmed by this, that Ture's sons were demonstrably related to Ulf Abjörnsson (sparre) known from the time of King Magnus Eriksson.\"\n\nhttps://sok.riksarkivet.se/sbl/Presentation.aspx?id=18188\n\n\n\"Ture Kettilsson (son av Kettil, Tab. 1), död före 1327-02-29. Riddare och riksråd. Lagman i Värend. Gift med Sigrid (sparre), möjligen dotter av med den från konung Magnus Erikssons tid bekante Ulf Abjörnsson (sparre).\"\n\n\"Ture Kettilsson (son of Kettil, Tab. 1), died before 1327-02-29. Knight and councilor. Lawman in Värend. Married to Sigrid (sparrow), possibly daughter of Ulf Abjörnsson, known from the time of King Magnus Eriksson (chevron).\"\n\nhttps://www.adelsvapen.com/genealogi/Bielke_af_%C3%85ker%C3%B6_nr_8#TAB_4","sourceList":[{"title":"Wikitree - Ture Kettilsson","sourceType":"DEFAULT","sourceLink":"https://www.wikitree.com/wiki/Kettilsson-3","sourceUri":"QHGW-PV1"},{"title":"Adelsvapen - Ture Kettilsson","sourceType":"DEFAULT","sourceLink":"https://www.adelsvapen.com/genealogi/Bielke_af_%C3%85ker%C3%B6_nr_8#TAB_4","sourceUri":"QHGW-LND"},{"title":"Svenskt biografiskt lexikon - Ture Kettilsson (Bielke)","sourceType":"DEFAULT","sourceLink":"https://sok.riksarkivet.se/Sbl/Presentation.aspx?id=18188","sourceUri":"SZLC-KQB"}],"events":[{"name":"Birth","sources":"0","year":"1260","date":"1260"},{"name":"Birth of Child","sources":"0","year":"1290","date":"Abt 1290","place":"Sweden","age":"30","id":"MCPD-C1C"},{"name":"Birth of Child","sources":"0","year":"1290","date":"Abt 1290","place":"Sweden","age":"30","id":"M4WS-6LR"},{"name":"Death","sources":"0","year":"1327","date":"29 March 1327","place":"Kråkerum, Mönsterås, Kalmar, Sverige","age":"67"}],"parent":[{"name":"Kettil","gender":"Male","lifespan":"–Male","@type":"Person","identifier":"27NL-NBL","url":"https://ancestors.familysearch.org/en/27NL-NBL/kettil-","published":true}],"sibling":[{"name":"Ture Kettilsson Bielke af Åkerö","gender":"Male","lifespan":"1260–1327","birthDate":"+1260","deathDate":"+1327-03-29","age":67,"portrait":